column38: I could see hopeful aspects in my future, so I didn't feel that there was nothing to be hopeful about.
column39: I didn't feel that life was meaningless.
column40: There were moments when I felt agitated, but it didn't happen all the time.
column41: I wasn't worried about situations where I might panic and make a fool of myself recently.
column42: I didn't experience any trembling in my hands recently.
column43: There were moments when I found it difficult to work up the initiative to do things, but it wasn't constant.
